        @Nullable
@CheckReturnValue
boolean validate(T object,
                                         @Nullable
                                         Exception e)
                 throws Exception
        Validate the object, return true if valid, false of throw an Exception with validation detail otherwise. in case of throwing an exception the object is considered invalid.
        Parameters:
        object - - object to validate.
        e - - exception previously encountered while handling the object.
        Returns:
        - true is object is still valid, false otherwise.
        Throws:
        Exception - - something happened during validation.
